OL,3,CRNLI rescues yacht in 'highly
OL,4,Cdangerous position' during gale-force
OL,5,Cwinds
OL,7,FAn inshore lifeboat saved one person
OL,8,Fon board a 40-foot (12.2meters) yacht
OL,9,Fon Monday afternoon, after multiple
OL,10,Freports of the vessel in serious
OL,11,Fdifficulty.
OL,13,FThe Stranraer RNLI launched the
OL,14,Flifeboat north of Loch Ryan at 5.59pm
OL,15,Fon January 12, into what "severe
OL,16,Fweather conditions" and gale-force
OL,17,Fwinds measuring Force 7.
