OL,3,CRNLI rescues yacht in 'highly
OL,4,Cdangerous position' during gale-force
OL,5,Cwinds
OL,7,FThe yacht's anchor system had failed,
OL,8,Fmeaning it had no way of holding its
OL,9,Fposition in the sea, or manoeuvring.
OL,10,FThe inshore lifeboat was launched to
OL,11,Freach the person on the boat, and
OL,12,Fstabilise the craft while further
OL,13,Fsupport was organised.
OL,15,FThe Stranraer RNLI described the
OL,16,Fweather on Monday as "very difficult",
OL,17,Fwith "strong winds, steep waves and
OL,18,Fdriving rain, conditions which made
OL,19,Fvisibility poor."
