OL,5,Cwinds
OL,7,FWhile the RNLI lifeboat travelled to
OL,8,Fthe vessel in distress, crew on board
OL,9,Fthe nearby Stena Superfast VII
OL,10,Fassisted by maintaining a continuous
OL,11,Fvisual watch on the drifting yacht,
OL,12,Frelaying position information to HM
OL,13,FCoastguard and the lifeboat crew.
OL,15,FOnce the lifeboat made it to the
OL,16,Fyacht, crews found it was rolling
OL,17,Fheavily to the wind and waves,
OL,18,Fincreasing the risk of it being
OL,19,Fknocked down or swamped by the storm.
