OL,3,CRNLI rescues yacht in 'highly
OL,4,Cdangerous position' during gale-force
OL,5,Cwinds
OL,7,FThe lifeboat crew used control lines
OL,8,Fto bring the yacht to face the sea,
OL,9,Fwhich reduced the yacht's rolling
OL,10,Fmotion, while the Girvan RNLI was
OL,11,Fcalled to bring its all-weather
OL,12,Flifeboat to tow the yacht to the
OL,13,Fsafety of Stranraer Marina.
OL,15,FOn arrival at the marina, HM
OL,16,FCoastguard teams helped the RNLI to
OL,17,Fsecure the vessel, while its sole
OL,18,Foccupant was brought to land safely
OL,19,Fand unharmed.
