OL,3,CRNLI rescues yacht in 'highly
OL,4,Cdangerous position' during gale-force
OL,5,Cwinds
OL,7,FAt 10pm Stranraer RNLI's lifeboat was
OL,8,Frecovered and refuelled, ready for
OL,9,Fmore call outs.
OL,11,FA Stranraer RNLI spokesperson said:
OL,12,F"This was a challenging service
OL,13,Fcarried out in very difficult weather.
OL,14,FThe yacht was being driven by strong
OL,15,Fwinds and heavy seas after its anchor
OL,16,Ffailed, and the situation was
OL,17,Fdeteriorating.
