OL,3,CRNLI rescues yacht in 'highly
OL,4,Cdangerous position' during gale-force
OL,5,Cwinds
OL,7,F"Our volunteer crew worked calmly and
OL,8,Fprofessionally in demanding conditions
OL,9,Fto bring the vessel head-to-sea and
OL,10,Fstabilise it until Girvan's all-
OL,11,Fweather lifeboat could arrive to
OL,12,Fcomplete the tow.
OL,14,F"We are very grateful to HM Coastguard
OL,15,Fand to the crew of Stena Superfast VII
OL,16,Ffor their excellent support and
OL,17,Fcoordination, which played a vital
OL,18,Frole in bringing this incident to a
OL,19,Fsafe conclusion."
